net.proteusframework.core.usertype

Class LocalizedObjectKeyUserType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.type.AbstractType
      • net.proteusframework.core.usertype.LocalizedObjectKeyUserType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, BasicType, Type

    @Configurable
public class LocalizedObjectKeyUserType
extends AbstractType
implements BasicType
    A Type for storing i18n key from a LocalizedObjectKey as a long.

    This is named a "UserType" for backward compatibility.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@proteus.co)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
